im u'^4/(\\ell_{\\bot}^2 Ro_{\\varepsilon}^{0.62}\n\\tau_{nl})$, where $\\ell_{\\bot}$ is the integral length-scale in the direction\nnormal to the axis of rotation and $\\tau_{nl}$ is the non-liner time-scale of\nthe initial homogeneous isotropic field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jul 2019 21:11:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-20"}
