ds on centrality and a good agreement with predictions are\nobserved for mid-central and central collisions. For peripheral collisions, the\ndata agree with predictions within 1.7 (0.9) standard deviations for $W^-$\n($W^+$) bosons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Jul 2019 12:57:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2019 15:08:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-25"}
