that our research will be a starting point\nfor efficient planetary defense against large PHAs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Jul 2019 12:11:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Mar 2020 03:44:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 8 Apr 2020 03:28:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-09"}
